-bash-3.2$
+---+

** Use <<<shell.sourceforge.net>>> (instead of <<<web.sourceforge.net>>>) in you site URL

  In the project's <<<pom.xml>>>:

+---+
  ...
  <distributionManagement>
    ...
    <site>
      <id>qifcon.sf.net</id>
      <url>scp://shell.sourceforge.net/home/groups/q/qi/qifcon/htdocs</url>
    </site>
  </distributionManagement>
  ...
+---+

